      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Standardizing Column Names\n",
        "\n",
        "To make the code cleaner and reduce errors, I standardize the column names by replacing spaces with underscores and removing special characters where needed."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "kapP9xoBin0T"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Standardize column names\n",
        "df.columns = (\n",
        "    df.columns\n",
        "    .str.strip()\n",
        "    .str.replace(\" \", \"_\")\n",
        "    .str.replace(\"/\", \"_\")\n",
        "    .str.replace(\"-\", \"_\")\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(df.columns.tolist())"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "sEcoKzAOiq4u",
