    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Data Cleaning: Duplicates and Missing Values\n",
        "\n",
        "Before building models, I check for duplicate rows and missing values. Duplicate records can bias results, while missing values can break modeling steps or reduce model quality if not handled properly."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "LB2PJWg2itLc"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Check duplicates\n",
        "print(\"Duplicate rows before removal:\", df.duplicated().sum())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Remove duplicates\n",
        "df = df.drop_duplicates()\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Shape after removing duplicates:\", df.shape)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "Z3g64RcRisjS",
        "outputId": "0ca09b2f-0824-4f82-bad0-1798f50c383f"
      },
      "execution_count": 6,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Duplicate rows before removal: 715\n",
            "Shape after removing duplicates: (11199, 16)\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Missing values before cleaning\n",
        "missing_before = df.isnull().sum().sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
        "missing_before[missing_before > 0]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 241
        },
        "id": "QzlNjeU3iywK",
