        "# Conclusion\n",
        "\n",
        "## Are you satisfied with the final model's performance? Why or why not?\n",
        "\n",
        "Overall, I am **moderately satisfied** with the final model’s performance. The model achieves an **R² of 0.4487 on the test set and 0.516 on the training set**, meaning it explains roughly **45–52% of the variation in MSRP**. This is a meaningful improvement over the simple regression models, confirming that combining multiple variables significantly improves predictive power.\n",
